    {"slug": "e15-699", "title": "Criticize the old world and build a new world with Mao Zedong Thought as a weapon, 1966", "title_zh": "\u4ee5\u6bdb\u6cfd\u4e1c\u601d\u60f3\u4e3a\u6b66\u5668\u6279\u5224\u65e7\u4e16\u754c\u5efa\u8bbe\u65b0\u4e16\u754c", "title_pinyin": "Yi Mao Zedong sixiang wei wuqi pipan jiu shijie jianshe xin shijie", "year": "1966, September", "theme": "Cultural Revolution (1966-1968)", "designer": "Shanghai People's Fine Arts Publishing House Propaganda Poster Group (\u4e0a\u6d77\u4eba\u6c11\u7f8e\u672f\u51fa\u7248\u793e\u5ba3\u4f20\u753b\u7ec4)", "call_number": "BG E15/699", "collection": "Landsberger collection", "description": "features quotations from Mao\u2019s writings. It is small and bound in a red plastic cover so you can always carry it with you. A good Red Guard knows the book by heart and rarely reads anything else.", "image_url": "https://chineseposters.net/sites/default/files/images/e15-699.jpg", "page_url": "https://chineseposters.net/gallery/e15-699"},
    {"slug": "e15-183", "title": "Hold high the great red flag of Mao Zedong Thought, thoroughly smash the reactionary line of Liu and Deng, ca. 1966", "title_zh": "\u9ad8\u4e3e\u6bdb\u6cfd\u4e1c\u601d\u60f3\u4f1f\u5927\u7ea2\u65d7, \u5f7b\u5e95\u7c89\u788e\u5218\u9093\u7684\u53cd\u52a8\u8def\u7ebf", "title_pinyin": "Gaoju Mao Zedong sixiang weida hongqi, chedi fensui Liu Dengde fandong luxian", "year": "ca. 1966", "theme": "Cultural Revolution (1966-1968)", "designer": "", "call_number": "BG E15/183", "collection": "Landsberger collection", "description": ". Liu is accused of wanting to take Mao's place, Deng's economic reforms are abhorrent to Mao. Both are\u00a0exiled to the countryside. Liu dies in 1969, Deng survives and is rehabilitated in 1973.", "image_url": "https://chineseposters.net/sites/default/files/images/e15-183.jpg", "page_url": "https://chineseposters.net/gallery/e15-183"},
    {"slug": "e15-179", "title": "Thoroughly expose Ulanfu\u2019s anti-Party clique, ca. 1966", "title_zh": "\u5f7b\u5e95\u6233\u7a7f\u4e4c\u5170\u592b\u53cd\u515a\u96c6\u56e2", "title_pinyin": "Chedi chuochuan Ulanfu fandang jituan", "year": "ca. 1966", "theme": "Cultural Revolution (1966-1968)", "designer": "Hohhot Revolutionary Rebel Liaison Headquarters Fine Arts Group (\u547c\u548c\u6d69\u7279\u9769\u547d\u9020\u53cd\u8054\u7edc\u603b\u90e8\u7f8e\u672f\u7ec4)", "call_number": "BG E15/179", "collection": "Landsberger collection", "description": "Ulanfu, an ethnic Mongol, first party secretary of the Inner Mongolian Autonomous Region and alternate Politburo member, was among the first high Party officials to fall. He was dismissed in August 1966 and accused of being \u2018the biggest party power-holder taking the capitalist ro", "image_url": "https://chineseposters.net/sites/default/files/images/e15-179.jpg", "page_url": "https://chineseposters.net/gallery/e15-179"},
